00:00:17.484 --> 00:00:18.777 line:90%
Why…

00:00:20.695 --> 00:00:22.614 line:90%
do you resent Father?

00:00:26.409 --> 00:00:28.078 line:90%
You killed Prince Yeongan

00:00:29.329 --> 00:00:31.873 line:90%
and now seek to harm even Father. Why?

00:00:32.374 --> 00:00:33.500 line:90%
Look closely.

00:00:37.295 --> 00:00:38.380 line:90%
See…

00:00:40.382 --> 00:00:42.634 line:90%
how I came to die.

00:00:54.521 --> 00:00:57.524 line:90%
Father poisoned me.

00:01:03.822 --> 00:01:05.532 line:90%
Father…

00:01:07.534 --> 00:01:08.368 line:90%
killed me.

00:01:10.662 --> 00:01:13.456 line:90%
-Your Majesty, you are awake!
-Your Majesty.

00:01:20.171 --> 00:01:22.299 line:90%
-Chief Eunuch Kim.
-Yes, Your Majesty.

00:01:22.382 --> 00:01:24.509 line:90%
Summon the Chief Royal Secretary.

00:01:27.137 --> 00:01:27.971 line:90%
Your Majesty.

00:01:30.891 --> 00:01:32.183 line:90%
There is no time.

00:01:34.811 --> 00:01:39.232 line:90%
The pestilence must be contained at once.
Carry out the edict as it is written.

00:01:43.737 --> 00:01:44.779 line:90%
Your Majesty.

00:01:44.863 --> 00:01:48.658 line:90%
Are you ordering us
to kill everyone in the village?

00:01:48.742 --> 00:01:51.077 line:90%
PUT THEM ALL TO DEATH

00:01:53.330 --> 00:01:54.873 line:90%
Do not delay.

00:01:56.124 --> 00:01:57.876 line:90%
<i>He is an ak-gwi.</i>

00:02:00.086 --> 00:02:02.005 line:90%
<i>A living ak-gwi.</i>

00:02:03.548 --> 00:02:05.675 line:90%
Father killed me.

00:02:07.218 --> 00:02:10.472 line:90%
Father killed me
when I learned of his sins.

00:02:18.396 --> 00:02:22.400 line:90%
Since you know the secret as well,
he will kill you.

00:02:23.193 --> 00:02:24.694 line:90%
-I am next.
-You are next.

00:02:24.778 --> 00:02:29.574 line:90%
You know the secret. Father killed me.
Father poisoned me. You are next.

00:02:29.658 --> 00:02:31.868 line:90%
-He will kill me too.
-He will kill you soon.

00:02:33.370 --> 00:02:35.497 line:90%
-You know the secret.
-Because I know the truth as well.

00:02:35.580 --> 00:02:37.499 line:90%
Father killed everyone.

00:02:38.917 --> 00:02:42.545 line:90%
THE EAST PALACE

00:02:42.629 --> 00:02:44.547 line:90%
<i>You are next.</i>

00:03:01.606 --> 00:03:03.066 line:90%
Damn it.

00:03:04.275 --> 00:03:06.444 line:90%
Even here, I still cannot see clearly.

00:03:50.780 --> 00:03:51.823 line:90%
Princess.

00:04:07.172 --> 00:04:10.133 line:90%
You defied my order
to save Prince Yeongan.

00:04:10.633 --> 00:04:14.179 line:90%
And yet you hid here, deceiving me

00:04:15.055 --> 00:04:17.140 line:90%
and taking me for a fool?

00:04:17.223 --> 00:04:20.226 line:90%
That is how I saved Your Majesty
from the spirit.

00:04:20.310 --> 00:04:22.937 line:90%
I heard you even dug up
the body of the Crown Prince.

00:04:23.480 --> 00:04:24.773 line:90%
Where is the body now?

00:04:24.856 --> 00:04:27.108 line:90%
I cannot tell you.

00:04:27.609 --> 00:04:30.945 line:90%
It is necessary to banish the spirit.

00:04:31.029 --> 00:04:32.072 line:90%
For that spirit is

00:04:32.655 --> 00:04:34.365 line:90%
your son, Your Majesty.

00:04:39.120 --> 00:04:40.371 line:90%
You have ten days.

00:04:41.206 --> 00:04:44.084 line:90%
-Banish the spirit within that time.
-Ten days are not enough.

00:04:44.167 --> 00:04:45.251 line:90%
I said ten days.

00:04:45.335 --> 00:04:48.880 line:90%
Then you must do as I say as well,
Your Majesty.

00:04:48.963 --> 00:04:50.715 line:90%
Mind your tongue. How dare you--

00:04:50.799 --> 00:04:53.718 line:90%
I will place a ward in your bedchamber.

00:04:53.802 --> 00:04:56.096 line:90%
It is to keep the spirit from entering.

00:04:56.679 --> 00:04:58.598 line:90%
Unless you wish to cough up blood

00:04:59.808 --> 00:05:02.477 line:90%
and be at death's door again.

00:05:14.989 --> 00:05:16.241 line:90%
Very well.

00:05:16.825 --> 00:05:17.700 line:90%
On one condition.

00:05:19.327 --> 00:05:21.538 line:90%
Place it outside the palace hall.

00:05:56.281 --> 00:05:57.115 line:90%
Princess.

00:05:58.992 --> 00:05:59.993 line:90%
Princess.

00:06:02.370 --> 00:06:04.455 line:90%
Princess!

00:06:07.292 --> 00:06:08.376 line:90%
It cannot be…

00:06:12.547 --> 00:06:14.632 line:90%
Princess, are you all right?

00:06:27.353 --> 00:06:28.354 line:90%
Are you awake?

00:06:35.778 --> 00:06:37.363 line:90%
What happened?

00:06:38.239 --> 00:06:39.657 line:90%
You fainted.

00:06:41.868 --> 00:06:45.788 line:90%
It appears the spirit of the Crown Prince
took hold of you.

00:06:47.665 --> 00:06:50.877 line:90%
He used your body to hide his own.

00:06:52.837 --> 00:06:53.755 line:90%
Then

00:06:54.631 --> 00:06:56.507 line:90%
is he still attached to me?

00:06:56.591 --> 00:06:58.092 line:90%
I do not know.

00:06:59.844 --> 00:07:01.054 line:90%
What do you mean?

00:07:03.640 --> 00:07:06.809 line:90%
I injured my eyes in the Realm of Gwi,
so I cannot see spirits.

00:07:09.646 --> 00:07:11.314 line:90%
Get some rest for now.

00:07:12.232 --> 00:07:14.484 line:90%
I will look for the Crown Prince's body.

00:07:15.985 --> 00:07:17.195 line:90%
There is no need.

00:07:19.822 --> 00:07:21.282 line:90%
What do you mean?

00:07:22.242 --> 00:07:24.369 line:90%
Even if you find the body
and banish the spirit,

00:07:24.452 --> 00:07:27.330 line:90%
he will spare neither you nor me.

00:07:29.165 --> 00:07:31.000 line:90%
The man killed his own son.

00:07:34.462 --> 00:07:35.797 line:90%
Killed his own son?

00:07:40.593 --> 00:07:44.180 line:90%
<i>The rice in his mouth had turned black.</i>

00:07:46.391 --> 00:07:48.268 line:90%
He was poisoned.

00:07:53.481 --> 00:07:55.358 line:90%
To avoid ending up like the Crown Prince,

00:07:56.943 --> 00:07:59.862 line:90%
we must prove
that the incidents 30 years ago,

00:07:59.946 --> 00:08:02.824 line:90%
thought to be the spirit's curse,
were all Father's doing.

00:08:03.866 --> 00:08:06.911 line:90%
Before he kills more people.

00:08:07.787 --> 00:08:10.123 line:90%
I sent the soldiers
and carried out your command.

00:08:10.623 --> 00:08:15.003 line:90%
However, it appears some of them
released women and children,

00:08:15.086 --> 00:08:16.713 line:90%
allowing them to escape.

00:08:23.386 --> 00:08:27.181 line:90%
Are those who released the villagers
still there?

00:08:28.099 --> 00:08:29.684 line:90%
Yes, Your Majesty.

00:08:30.184 --> 00:08:33.938 line:90%
Then seize them,
and in front of the other soldiers…

00:08:36.482 --> 00:08:37.942 line:90%
behead them.

00:08:44.073 --> 00:08:45.283 line:90%
I suppose

00:08:46.075 --> 00:08:49.120 line:90%
I will have to meet
the spirit of the Crown Prince.

00:08:50.288 --> 00:08:51.706 line:90%
What do you mean?

00:08:51.789 --> 00:08:56.502 line:90%
I must ask him myself
how he came to know of Father's sins.

00:08:57.879 --> 00:08:59.505 line:90%
He may be asking for my help

00:09:00.173 --> 00:09:02.508 line:90%
so he can ease his resentment.

00:09:02.592 --> 00:09:03.551 line:90%
Princess,

00:09:04.218 --> 00:09:06.346 line:90%
he is already an ak-gwi
who has killed people.

00:09:07.180 --> 00:09:08.556 line:90%
Forget about it.

00:09:09.098 --> 00:09:10.224 line:90%
Just make this.

00:09:13.895 --> 00:09:15.563 line:90%
What is this?

00:09:15.646 --> 00:09:20.610 line:90%
A ward to keep the spirit
of the Crown Prince from clinging to you.

00:09:38.086 --> 00:09:39.712 line:90%
It must be very frustrating

00:09:40.755 --> 00:09:42.298 line:90%
not being able to see well.

00:09:44.384 --> 00:09:45.593 line:90%
There is one good thing.

00:09:47.011 --> 00:09:50.306 line:90%
For the first time in my life,
I see no spirits or gwi-mae at all.

00:09:51.224 --> 00:09:53.393 line:90%
So I find it nice.

00:10:00.358 --> 00:10:01.651 line:90%
Then do you wish to

00:10:03.444 --> 00:10:05.446 line:90%
go on living like this?

00:10:07.365 --> 00:10:08.658 line:90%
Even if you can barely see?

00:10:11.452 --> 00:10:13.371 line:90%
Well, whatever my wishes may be,

00:10:14.330 --> 00:10:17.458 line:90%
I must regain my sight so we can find
the spirit of the Crown Prince.

00:10:18.793 --> 00:10:20.753 line:90%
Only then will we both survive.

00:10:44.152 --> 00:10:46.237 line:90%
What are you doing?

00:10:48.197 --> 00:10:50.116 line:90%
I am checking
if the spirit of the Crown Prince

00:10:50.700 --> 00:10:52.952 line:90%
has secretly clung to you.

00:10:54.787 --> 00:10:56.873 line:90%
But now that I can barely see,

00:10:56.956 --> 00:10:59.041 line:90%
I could never tell.

00:10:59.959 --> 00:11:01.252 line:90%
Good grief.

00:11:08.801 --> 00:11:10.553 line:90%
About your sight…

00:11:13.055 --> 00:11:16.142 line:90%
How can you regain it?

00:11:16.225 --> 00:11:19.270 line:90%
I must find the damn shaman
who got in my way.

00:11:21.105 --> 00:11:23.858 line:90%
Whoever wants the King dead
must be keeping that shaman.

00:11:27.361 --> 00:11:29.071 line:90%
Does anyone come to mind?

00:11:37.538 --> 00:11:40.291 line:90%
What brings you here?

00:11:40.958 --> 00:11:42.627 line:90%
I have something to ask you.

00:11:42.710 --> 00:11:44.712 line:90%
Have you held a shamanic ritual lately?

00:11:45.213 --> 00:11:46.506 line:90%
A shamanic ritual?

00:11:47.006 --> 00:11:50.968 line:90%
I believe you summoned a shaman
when Prince Yeongan collapsed.

00:11:51.469 --> 00:11:53.221 line:90%
Where is that shaman?

00:11:53.304 --> 00:11:56.849 line:90%
You came to see me just to ask that?

00:11:57.433 --> 00:12:00.895 line:90%
After what you did to me,

00:12:02.396 --> 00:12:04.774 line:90%
you still dare to stand before me.

00:12:07.026 --> 00:12:08.236 line:90%
Your Majesty.

00:12:21.082 --> 00:12:22.333 line:90%
More importantly…

00:12:26.462 --> 00:12:31.092 line:90%
that must be the feng shui master
His Majesty brought in.

00:12:31.175 --> 00:12:33.344 line:90%
Why have you brought him here?

00:12:33.844 --> 00:12:36.806 line:90%
He is inspecting the palace
at His Majesty's command.

00:12:36.889 --> 00:12:39.767 line:90%
-So the Queen Dowager's residence--
-You speak nothing but lies.

00:12:40.434 --> 00:12:44.146 line:90%
I know he has been up to
something strange.

00:12:46.440 --> 00:12:48.693 line:90%
Say it yourself.

00:12:48.776 --> 00:12:50.111 line:90%
Is there still

00:12:50.945 --> 00:12:54.782 line:90%
a spirit in the palace
that preys upon the royal bloodline?

00:12:54.865 --> 00:12:55.950 line:90%
A spirit in the palace?

00:12:56.033 --> 00:12:57.994 line:90%
If Uncle were to hear this,
he would laugh.

00:12:58.077 --> 00:12:59.662 line:90%
What did you just say?!

00:13:01.330 --> 00:13:03.374 line:90%
Whether it was the work
of a spirit or not,

00:13:03.457 --> 00:13:06.794 line:90%
it is a relief
that His Majesty has recovered, is it not?

00:13:07.420 --> 00:13:10.047 line:90%
Especially when pestilence spreads
across the land.

00:13:10.131 --> 00:13:13.301 line:90%
Princess, have you heard as well?

00:13:13.384 --> 00:13:18.347 line:90%
His Majesty sent soldiers
to where the pestilence had broken out.

00:13:18.431 --> 00:13:19.599 line:90%
And then…

00:13:22.560 --> 00:13:24.562 line:90%
he had everyone put to death.

00:13:32.194 --> 00:13:35.448 line:90%
Children and elders alike, every last one.

00:13:46.292 --> 00:13:47.752 line:90%
<i>He is an ak-gwi.</i>

00:13:49.545 --> 00:13:51.047 line:90%
<i>A living ak-gwi.</i>

00:13:53.174 --> 00:13:57.136 line:90%
<i>They say it was the first thing</i>
<i>His Majesty did upon waking.</i>

00:13:58.804 --> 00:14:00.473 line:90%
Mother!

00:14:03.100 --> 00:14:07.063 line:90%
Mother, please wake up.

00:14:07.563 --> 00:14:09.774 line:90%
<i>Father killed me.</i>

00:14:09.857 --> 00:14:12.610 line:90%
<i>You know the secret.</i>
<i>He will kill everyone.</i>

00:14:12.693 --> 00:14:14.904 line:90%
<i>You are next. Father killed me.</i>

00:14:14.987 --> 00:14:16.822 line:90%
<i>You are next.</i>

00:14:20.201 --> 00:14:22.328 line:90%
What do you think you are doing
to the Princess?

00:14:26.499 --> 00:14:28.834 line:90%
There was a centipede as big as a snake.

00:14:29.835 --> 00:14:31.754 line:90%
Perhaps the vermin are gathering here.

00:14:36.050 --> 00:14:39.970 line:90%
Uncle, did you come here
to report this matter to Her Majesty?

00:14:40.054 --> 00:14:43.307 line:90%
Why would I concern myself with it
when I hold no office?

00:14:43.849 --> 00:14:46.143 line:90%
His Majesty has issued an edict

00:14:46.227 --> 00:14:49.146 line:90%
that he will appoint my eldest son
as Crown Prince,

00:14:49.230 --> 00:14:51.232 line:90%
so I came to pay my respects…

00:14:53.442 --> 00:14:55.528 line:90%
to Her Majesty the Queen Dowager.

00:15:02.660 --> 00:15:06.997 line:90%
<i>Bring Prince Iksang's son, Prince Inha,</i>
<i>into the palace to learn court etiquette</i>

00:15:07.540 --> 00:15:11.001 line:90%
<i>and hold the Crown Prince investiture</i>
<i>as soon as possible.</i>

00:15:12.086 --> 00:15:13.921 line:90%
<i>With the land in turmoil,</i>

00:15:14.547 --> 00:15:17.091 line:90%
<i>we cannot leave the East Palace vacant</i>
<i>any longer.</i>

00:15:17.967 --> 00:15:22.972 line:90%
<i>I will take Prince Inha as my son</i>
<i>and seat him upon the throne.</i>

00:15:25.141 --> 00:15:26.559 line:90%
<i>He will kill me.</i>

00:15:27.601 --> 00:15:28.936 line:90%
<i>He will.</i>

00:15:29.812 --> 00:15:31.564 line:90%
<i>He is a man</i>

00:15:32.356 --> 00:15:34.400 line:90%
<i>who killed his own son.</i>

00:15:35.109 --> 00:15:36.360 line:90%
<i>That would mean</i>

00:15:37.111 --> 00:15:38.362 line:90%
<i>even I could be…</i>

00:15:39.488 --> 00:15:42.825 line:90%
RABBIT

00:15:48.622 --> 00:15:51.000 line:90%
What are you doing?

00:15:51.542 --> 00:15:53.002 line:90%
Compose yourself.

00:15:53.085 --> 00:15:56.172 line:90%
Dark thoughts
will cause your mind to collapse.

00:15:56.672 --> 00:15:59.175 line:90%
What if a spirit slips in
through that crack?

00:16:01.427 --> 00:16:02.803 line:90%
Just set the ward.

00:16:03.721 --> 00:16:06.515 line:90%
I can barely see, so you must do it all.

00:16:16.859 --> 00:16:17.985 line:90%
Lower.

00:16:18.527 --> 00:16:20.446 line:90%
-Place it lower.
-I know.

00:16:21.280 --> 00:16:22.865 line:90%
It is already set low.

00:16:23.365 --> 00:16:24.366 line:90%
RABBIT

00:16:24.450 --> 00:16:27.369 line:90%
-I said--
-I will let this go as you can barely see.

00:16:36.003 --> 00:16:40.007 line:90%
But why the "rabbit" sign?
And upside down at that.

00:16:40.090 --> 00:16:42.426 line:90%
The Crown Prince was born
in the Year of the Rabbit.

00:16:42.927 --> 00:16:44.678 line:90%
With his sign upside down,

00:16:45.763 --> 00:16:48.849 line:90%
his soul cannot pass through here
without a body.

00:16:51.560 --> 00:16:53.270 line:90%
So be careful

00:16:54.104 --> 00:16:56.607 line:90%
unless you want him to take your body.

00:16:57.107 --> 00:16:59.109 line:90%
I had no other choice back then.

00:17:01.320 --> 00:17:03.656 line:90%
After hearing
that your father killed his own child,

00:17:04.156 --> 00:17:06.242 line:90%
how could you possibly remain sane?

00:17:10.538 --> 00:17:12.122 line:90%
I will say this again.

00:17:12.623 --> 00:17:15.209 line:90%
You must compose yourself.

00:17:18.337 --> 00:17:22.550 line:90%
If you cannot, remain close
to someone you can rely on.

00:17:31.684 --> 00:17:32.852 line:90%
There is someone.

00:17:32.935 --> 00:17:34.812 line:90%
Someone I can rely on.

00:17:44.071 --> 00:17:45.406 line:90%
Saeng-gang.

00:17:46.740 --> 00:17:47.992 line:90%
Where are you headed?

00:17:48.075 --> 00:17:49.535 line:90%
Have you been well?

00:17:50.035 --> 00:17:52.538 line:90%
-You do not look so good.
-Good for her.

00:17:53.038 --> 00:17:55.040 line:90%
You are leaving the palace?

00:17:55.624 --> 00:17:58.377 line:90%
I came to care for Prince Yeongan,

00:17:58.460 --> 00:18:00.462 line:90%
yet I cannot do that anymore, can I?

00:18:00.963 --> 00:18:05.009 line:90%
With you and Gu-cheon here,
His Majesty should be safe.

00:18:05.593 --> 00:18:06.427 line:90%
However,

00:18:06.927 --> 00:18:09.179 line:90%
the matter of the late Crown Prince…

00:18:09.847 --> 00:18:12.850 line:90%
It is hard to believe
he has become a spirit, is it not?

00:18:18.606 --> 00:18:22.651 line:90%
This palace is truly a frightening place.

00:18:23.235 --> 00:18:25.404 line:90%
It does not suit an old woman like me.

00:18:28.824 --> 00:18:30.534 line:90%
He looks just like a corpse.

00:18:30.618 --> 00:18:32.411 line:90%
He cannot even eat or speak.

00:18:32.912 --> 00:18:36.582 line:90%
A shaman who lost their presiding deity
is as good as dead.

00:18:36.665 --> 00:18:38.083 line:90%
Good heavens, let us get going.

00:20:02.835 --> 00:20:04.461 line:90%
Take me in.

00:20:27.234 --> 00:20:30.279 line:90%
I shall be your new presiding deity.

00:20:30.821 --> 00:20:34.158 line:90%
Your Highness, the Crown Prince!

00:20:56.388 --> 00:20:57.806 line:90%
What happened?

00:21:00.893 --> 00:21:01.852 line:90%
My eyes.

00:21:02.936 --> 00:21:04.897 line:90%
I can no longer see at all.

00:21:08.942 --> 00:21:10.527 line:90%
That damn shaman

00:21:11.361 --> 00:21:13.822 line:90%
must have burned the object
that cursed my eyes.

00:21:13.906 --> 00:21:16.492 line:90%
Perhaps he has already taken in
a new presiding deity.

00:21:22.623 --> 00:21:24.666 line:90%
Then what do we do now?

00:21:25.292 --> 00:21:27.669 line:90%
Now that I cannot see spirits,

00:21:29.171 --> 00:21:31.006 line:90%
it is all over.

00:21:33.050 --> 00:21:35.094 line:90%
Is there any way to regain your sight?

00:21:39.932 --> 00:21:43.185 line:90%
There is one way,
but it is far too dangerous.

00:21:44.603 --> 00:21:45.854 line:90%
Why is that?

00:21:45.938 --> 00:21:48.816 line:90%
It means disturbing
what must not be disturbed.

00:21:57.032 --> 00:21:59.284 line:90%
But if that is the only way…

00:22:01.662 --> 00:22:02.496 line:90%
we must do it.

00:22:02.579 --> 00:22:03.664 line:90%
No.

00:22:04.373 --> 00:22:07.292 line:90%
I would rather flee the palace
than do that.

00:22:08.752 --> 00:22:11.505 line:90%
As long as I stay hidden, I will survive.

00:22:12.464 --> 00:22:14.633 line:90%
You cannot even see. Where would you go?

00:22:19.054 --> 00:22:20.597 line:90%
Since it has come to this,

00:22:21.473 --> 00:22:23.225 line:90%
you should flee the palace with me.

00:22:23.308 --> 00:22:26.854 line:90%
The moment we flee,
His Majesty will send troops to kill us.

00:22:27.437 --> 00:22:30.899 line:90%
And I do not wish to leave the palace
again for no fault of my own,

00:22:30.983 --> 00:22:32.609 line:90%
as I did as a child.

00:22:33.610 --> 00:22:37.197 line:90%
If you will not help me,
I shall find the Crown Prince myself.

00:22:37.281 --> 00:22:40.159 line:90%
I will find a way to save us both,
even alone.

00:22:40.242 --> 00:22:41.910 line:90%
How would you do that alone?

00:22:44.913 --> 00:22:46.957 line:90%
If the Crown Prince spirit comes near,

00:22:48.375 --> 00:22:49.459 line:90%
I will not stop it.

00:22:50.335 --> 00:22:52.838 line:90%
Do you understand how dangerous that is?

00:22:53.672 --> 00:22:55.799 line:90%
-If it takes your body--
-That will not happen.

00:22:56.508 --> 00:23:00.345 line:90%
His Majesty's sins must be proven
no matter what.

00:23:06.768 --> 00:23:08.562 line:90%
You have truly lost your mind.

00:23:21.241 --> 00:23:24.369 line:90%
Did you see the look
on the Princess's face?

00:23:25.287 --> 00:23:27.998 line:90%
Look on her face?

00:23:30.292 --> 00:23:35.380 line:90%
Did she not look
as if she were tormented by a spirit?

00:23:35.881 --> 00:23:39.301 line:90%
Could the spirit
of the Most Favored Lady of the Court

00:23:39.384 --> 00:23:42.346 line:90%
still remain in the palace?

00:23:42.429 --> 00:23:43.555 line:90%
No.

00:23:44.056 --> 00:23:48.936 line:90%
That man called Gu-cheon
surely banished it.

00:23:49.019 --> 00:23:50.812 line:90%
I feel lighter.

00:23:50.896 --> 00:23:53.774 line:90%
It means the resentment toward me is gone.

00:23:54.274 --> 00:23:56.443 line:90%
Yet Prince Yeongan is dead,

00:23:56.526 --> 00:23:58.987 line:90%
and both His Majesty and the Princess
have fallen ill.

00:24:04.284 --> 00:24:09.998 line:90%
Could it be another spirit
that is after the King?

00:24:14.670 --> 00:24:15.712 line:90%
Your Majesty.

00:24:15.796 --> 00:24:19.883 line:90%
It was my shame that blinded me.

00:24:19.967 --> 00:24:23.178 line:90%
Of all the late King's sons,

00:24:23.262 --> 00:24:25.847 line:90%
why was the present King
the only one to survive?

00:24:25.931 --> 00:24:29.685 line:90%
How did he survive the curse alone?

00:24:31.603 --> 00:24:32.646 line:90%
<i>Yes.</i>

00:24:33.146 --> 00:24:35.315 line:90%
<i>There must be another reason.</i>

00:24:36.233 --> 00:24:40.779 line:90%
<i>There was a royal physician who examined</i>
<i>the dead Princes 30 years ago.</i>

00:24:41.280 --> 00:24:42.781 line:90%
<i>Find him.</i>

00:24:49.371 --> 00:24:51.039 line:90%
He is dead?

00:24:51.540 --> 00:24:53.083 line:90%
Yes, Your Majesty.

00:24:53.583 --> 00:24:57.504 line:90%
I traced the royal physician
who attended the Princes 30 years ago.

00:24:58.338 --> 00:25:00.173 line:90%
A few years after,

00:25:00.257 --> 00:25:03.260 line:90%
he suddenly coughed up dark blood
and died.

00:25:03.760 --> 00:25:07.431 line:90%
Those are the same symptoms
the dead Princes had, are they not?

00:25:10.058 --> 00:25:13.770 line:90%
Then it was not a spirit

00:25:14.563 --> 00:25:16.940 line:90%
that preyed upon the King's bloodline.

00:25:19.776 --> 00:25:20.777 line:90%
Pardon?

00:25:24.323 --> 00:25:27.492 line:90%
Where is the son of Prince Iksang
right now?

00:25:32.164 --> 00:25:35.083 line:90%
Prince Inha!

00:25:37.085 --> 00:25:38.337 line:90%
Summon the physician.

00:25:38.420 --> 00:25:39.296 line:90%
Yes, ma'am!

00:25:51.266 --> 00:25:52.809 line:90%
What is it at this late hour?

00:25:52.893 --> 00:25:55.520 line:90%
Her Majesty summons you, Your Highness.

00:25:55.604 --> 00:25:57.230 line:90%
For what reason?

00:25:58.106 --> 00:26:00.067 line:90%
Prince Inha has collapsed.

00:26:02.319 --> 00:26:04.446 line:90%
Then why have I been summoned?

00:26:05.113 --> 00:26:06.490 line:90%
In that chamber,

00:26:07.282 --> 00:26:08.700 line:90%
we found a refreshment box.

00:26:12.162 --> 00:26:16.500 line:90%
It bears the same pattern as the one
you once brought to Her Majesty.

00:26:17.793 --> 00:26:22.547 line:90%
Her Majesty says it appears he collapsed
after eating what was in that box.

00:26:28.595 --> 00:26:29.805 line:90%
Your Highness.

00:26:42.943 --> 00:26:43.944 line:90%
<i>Saeng-gang.</i>

00:26:45.946 --> 00:26:47.155 line:90%
<i>Saeng-gang.</i>

00:26:47.239 --> 00:26:48.573 line:90%
Saeng-gang!

00:26:49.658 --> 00:26:50.700 line:90%
Saeng-gang.

00:26:52.869 --> 00:26:55.330 line:90%
What is wrong with you?
Have you come to your senses?

00:26:57.749 --> 00:26:59.376 line:90%
Why am I here?

00:26:59.459 --> 00:27:00.877 line:90%
I should be asking you that.

00:27:01.378 --> 00:27:04.047 line:90%
You appeared out of nowhere
and just stood there.

00:27:04.131 --> 00:27:05.966 line:90%
I should take my leave now.

00:27:09.719 --> 00:27:12.931 line:90%
What on earth is going on?
You can tell me.

00:27:17.894 --> 00:27:19.104 line:90%
Grandmother.

00:27:21.022 --> 00:27:22.399 line:90%
Father…

00:27:24.484 --> 00:27:26.445 line:90%
intends to begin again.

00:27:27.863 --> 00:27:28.697 line:90%
To become

00:27:29.531 --> 00:27:31.533 line:90%
the pond spirit himself.

00:27:32.492 --> 00:27:34.035 line:90%
The pond spirit?

00:27:34.536 --> 00:27:36.955 line:90%
The one who killed his brothers
30 years ago…

00:27:39.458 --> 00:27:40.500 line:90%
was Father.

00:27:41.418 --> 00:27:42.252 line:90%
What…

00:27:44.171 --> 00:27:46.798 line:90%
-What are you talking--
-But he means to do it again.

00:27:47.841 --> 00:27:49.759 line:90%
He intends to kill someone.

00:27:50.969 --> 00:27:54.097 line:90%
He summoned Prince Iksang's son
to the palace and poisoned him.

00:27:58.685 --> 00:27:59.936 line:90%
That cannot be.

00:28:00.020 --> 00:28:03.106 line:90%
There was a lotus-patterned
refreshment box in his quarters.

00:28:03.190 --> 00:28:04.524 line:90%
Mother also died

00:28:06.443 --> 00:28:09.279 line:90%
after eating what was in that box.

00:28:10.489 --> 00:28:12.365 line:90%
-That is impossible.
-No!

00:28:13.408 --> 00:28:17.621 line:90%
Grandmother, you noticed something strange
about Father as well, did you not?

00:28:17.704 --> 00:28:19.873 line:90%
If you know anything, please tell me.

00:28:19.956 --> 00:28:22.042 line:90%
Father must be stopped no matter what.

00:28:22.125 --> 00:28:23.335 line:90%
If there is no other way,

00:28:24.669 --> 00:28:26.796 line:90%
we must have him step down
from the throne.

00:28:46.066 --> 00:28:47.901 line:90%
Forgive me.

00:28:48.985 --> 00:28:50.153 line:90%
<i>Disappeared?</i>

00:28:50.237 --> 00:28:51.363 line:90%
What?

00:28:51.446 --> 00:28:53.198 line:90%
Was she not here to see you?

00:28:53.281 --> 00:28:55.242 line:90%
Then where did she go?

00:28:56.451 --> 00:28:58.286 line:90%
Tell me again from the beginning.

00:29:03.625 --> 00:29:09.005 line:90%
The moment she heard from Lady Jang
that Prince Inha had collapsed,

00:29:09.089 --> 00:29:13.093 line:90%
she pushed past the people there
and went off somewhere.

00:29:13.176 --> 00:29:14.844 line:90%
They say she was not herself,

00:29:15.345 --> 00:29:18.974 line:90%
as if she had lost her mind.

00:29:23.853 --> 00:29:25.939 line:90%
She has collapsed inside.

00:29:27.566 --> 00:29:30.193 line:90%
Do you know where the Princess might be?

00:29:30.694 --> 00:29:32.153 line:90%
<i>I do.</i>

00:29:32.737 --> 00:29:34.990 line:90%
<i>A place where there is someone</i>
<i>she can rely on.</i>

00:29:39.327 --> 00:29:42.289 line:90%
But does that man, Gu-cheon,

00:29:43.331 --> 00:29:45.417 line:90%
know about this?

00:29:48.044 --> 00:29:49.212 line:90%
No, he does not.

00:29:50.255 --> 00:29:52.257 line:90%
Only I, who can hear the voice of spirits,

00:29:53.842 --> 00:29:55.302 line:90%
know about this.

00:30:00.640 --> 00:30:01.891 line:90%
That is a lie.

00:30:07.480 --> 00:30:08.690 line:90%
Pardon?

00:30:10.984 --> 00:30:12.360 line:90%
<i>Saeng-gang.</i>

00:30:17.198 --> 00:30:18.533 line:90%
Mother?

00:30:42.349 --> 00:30:43.767 line:90%
Protective sutras…

00:30:44.809 --> 00:30:47.395 line:90%
<i>Stay away from her.</i>

00:30:52.984 --> 00:30:54.986 line:90%
<i>Stay away from her. Spirits do not exist.</i>

00:30:55.070 --> 00:30:59.199 line:90%
<i>One day, everyone will know</i>
<i>that you are the pond spirit.</i>

00:31:00.158 --> 00:31:03.078 line:90%
It seems your mother is outside.

00:31:03.161 --> 00:31:07.457 line:90%
When will she ever stop following me?
This is why I did not want to come here.

00:31:11.628 --> 00:31:12.462 line:90%
Are there

00:31:13.338 --> 00:31:15.423 line:90%
other spirits outside as well?

00:31:17.300 --> 00:31:18.468 line:90%
<i>Saeng-gang.</i>

00:31:19.636 --> 00:31:21.805 line:90%
<i>Stay away from her.</i>

00:31:28.812 --> 00:31:31.731 line:90%
The serpent's cast skin killed
the dragon's child.

00:31:31.815 --> 00:31:34.526 line:90%
The serpent's cast skin killed
the dragon's child.

00:31:36.820 --> 00:31:39.155 line:90%
<i>It is dangerous, Saeng-gang.</i>

00:31:39.239 --> 00:31:42.075 line:90%
Your Grace.

00:31:42.158 --> 00:31:45.245 line:90%
No one can find out about this poison.

00:31:50.750 --> 00:31:51.918 line:90%
When I was a child…

00:31:54.003 --> 00:31:57.340 line:90%
you always came to see Mother and me
after we were cast out of the palace.

00:31:58.299 --> 00:32:02.554 line:90%
You would bring food
wrapped in cloths and boxes.

00:32:14.649 --> 00:32:16.609 line:90%
The one who poisoned Mother…

00:32:18.820 --> 00:32:19.863 line:90%
Was it you?

00:32:22.699 --> 00:32:23.575 line:90%
That is right.

00:32:23.658 --> 00:32:24.909 line:90%
You just

00:32:25.410 --> 00:32:26.911 line:90%
drank the same thing.

00:32:28.872 --> 00:32:30.999 line:90%
Since it was a weaker poison,

00:32:31.624 --> 00:32:34.085 line:90%
you will not die as the Princes did.

00:32:40.759 --> 00:32:43.511 line:90%
You will only lie there
like a living corpse,

00:32:43.595 --> 00:32:46.181 line:90%
unable to speak for the rest of your life.

00:32:50.852 --> 00:32:52.437 line:90%
<i>Grandmother,</i>

00:32:52.979 --> 00:32:55.148 line:90%
<i>you were the pond spirit.</i>

00:32:58.526 --> 00:33:00.320 line:90%
-Your Highness!
-Your Highness!

00:33:00.403 --> 00:33:01.654 line:90%
Your Highness!

00:33:01.738 --> 00:33:03.573 line:90%
-Your Highness!
-Bring a stretcher!

00:33:03.656 --> 00:33:05.325 line:90%
Summon the physician now!

00:33:05.825 --> 00:33:08.244 line:90%
-Your Highness!
-Your Highness!

00:33:08.328 --> 00:33:10.163 line:90%
Your Highness!

00:33:21.549 --> 00:33:23.384 line:90%
I cannot believe he suddenly died

00:33:24.010 --> 00:33:25.470 line:90%
while riding a horse.

00:33:26.054 --> 00:33:28.181 line:90%
He had always been frail.

00:33:30.892 --> 00:33:32.685 line:90%
The Most Favored Lady of the Court,

00:33:32.769 --> 00:33:34.729 line:90%
who vowed
to end the royal bloodline, died,

00:33:35.396 --> 00:33:39.192 line:90%
and shortly after,
the Crown Prince was gone as well.

00:33:41.820 --> 00:33:43.988 line:90%
What a wonderful coincidence.

00:33:44.989 --> 00:33:46.574 line:90%
I have brought it, Your Grace.

00:33:47.325 --> 00:33:50.453 line:90%
No one can find out about this poison.

00:33:53.581 --> 00:33:55.542 line:90%
<i>We must make people believe</i>

00:33:55.625 --> 00:33:59.838 line:90%
<i>the Princes died from a curse of a spirit.</i>

00:34:02.006 --> 00:34:06.052 line:90%
<i>The pond spirit who cursed</i>
<i>the royal family and died.</i>

00:34:06.135 --> 00:34:07.470 line:90%
Your Majesty.

00:34:09.305 --> 00:34:11.432 line:90%
<i>The Queen,</i>

00:34:12.016 --> 00:34:14.727 line:90%
<i>who turned the Most Favored Lady</i>
<i>of the Court into a spirit,</i>

00:34:15.311 --> 00:34:17.397 line:90%
<i>must be blamed for all of this.</i>

00:34:18.022 --> 00:34:21.693 line:90%
THE SERPENT'S CAST SKIN
KILLED THE DRAGON'S CHILD

00:34:21.776 --> 00:34:25.446 line:90%
One of you must have defiled
the royal house.

00:34:33.121 --> 00:34:34.122 line:90%
<i>And</i>

00:34:35.081 --> 00:34:37.250 line:90%
<i>once all the other Princes are dead</i>…

00:34:39.752 --> 00:34:41.087 line:90%
<i>my son</i>

00:34:42.422 --> 00:34:43.965 line:90%
<i>will become the Crown Prince.</i>

00:34:50.680 --> 00:34:52.682 line:90%
<i>I must remove those</i>

00:34:53.600 --> 00:34:55.685 line:90%
<i>who might reveal the secret.</i>

00:34:56.311 --> 00:35:00.857 line:90%
<i>Anyone who would harm my son.</i>

00:35:02.734 --> 00:35:05.278 line:90%
<i>So is that why you killed Mother as well?</i>

00:35:05.862 --> 00:35:09.574 line:90%
Simply because she later learned
Father's secret?

00:35:09.657 --> 00:35:10.950 line:90%
Later?

00:35:12.160 --> 00:35:15.163 line:90%
Your mother was in on this with me
from the beginning.

00:35:33.973 --> 00:35:38.186 line:90%
<i>If not, how could your lowborn mother,</i>
<i>a mere court lady of the Saenggwabang,</i>

00:35:38.269 --> 00:35:40.813 line:90%
<i>have risen to the rank of consort?</i>

00:35:51.741 --> 00:35:55.745 line:90%
It is a throne your father and your mother
helped me build.

00:35:55.828 --> 00:35:57.455 line:90%
You, too,

00:35:58.289 --> 00:36:00.375 line:90%
are the product of that sin.

00:36:11.761 --> 00:36:13.554 line:90%
<i>He must be stopped.</i>

00:36:15.765 --> 00:36:17.433 line:90%
<i>We must prevent</i>

00:36:18.101 --> 00:36:19.519 line:90%
<i>any further sacrifice.</i>

00:36:21.104 --> 00:36:23.648 line:90%
<i>There was never any spirit to begin with.</i>

00:36:24.524 --> 00:36:27.318 line:90%
<i>There is no spirit that seeks to wipe out</i>
<i>the royal bloodline.</i>

00:36:28.903 --> 00:36:29.988 line:90%
<i>The King.</i>

00:36:30.488 --> 00:36:32.657 line:90%
<i>He is the living ak-gwi.</i>

00:36:32.740 --> 00:36:34.659 line:90%
<i>The King must be stopped.</i>

00:37:22.457 --> 00:37:24.751 line:90%
Saeng-gang.

00:37:32.967 --> 00:37:35.470 line:90%
So this is where spirits came through.

00:37:35.970 --> 00:37:39.140 line:90%
-Where has the Princess gone?
-I do not know.

00:37:39.640 --> 00:37:41.893 line:90%
More importantly, you should…

00:38:05.625 --> 00:38:07.210 line:90%
She threw away the ward.

00:38:09.712 --> 00:38:11.172 line:90%
It has collapsed.

00:38:23.142 --> 00:38:26.020 line:90%
What sin did you commit
to fear spirits so greatly

00:38:26.646 --> 00:38:30.274 line:90%
that you placed protective sutras
on every door?

00:38:33.569 --> 00:38:35.279 line:90%
Answer me!

00:38:35.363 --> 00:38:36.572 line:90%
What have you done

00:38:36.656 --> 00:38:39.659 line:90%
that your granddaughter lost her mind
and gave herself to a spirit?

00:38:54.924 --> 00:38:56.425 line:90%
What is that?

00:38:57.176 --> 00:38:58.052 line:90%
A straw effigy.

00:38:58.636 --> 00:39:01.055 line:90%
It will bear the ill fortune in my stead.

00:39:01.139 --> 00:39:02.640 line:90%
In your stead? What does it--

00:39:02.723 --> 00:39:04.267 line:90%
Hang this

00:39:05.560 --> 00:39:07.562 line:90%
exactly where I told you.

00:39:08.479 --> 00:39:10.898 line:90%
And what will you do in the meantime?

00:39:11.774 --> 00:39:13.276 line:90%
I will go save the Princess.

00:39:15.611 --> 00:39:18.614 line:90%
I warned her not to let the spirit
take hold of her.

00:39:19.532 --> 00:39:21.450 line:90%
How foolish and pathetic.

00:39:24.579 --> 00:39:25.413 line:90%
Here.

00:39:45.099 --> 00:39:47.018 line:90%
So it comes to this.

00:39:47.518 --> 00:39:49.937 line:90%
Damn my fate.

00:41:33.582 --> 00:41:34.583 line:90%
RABBIT

00:43:33.285 --> 00:43:34.578 line:90%
Please help her.

00:43:37.998 --> 00:43:39.291 line:90%
My Saeng-gang.

00:43:40.626 --> 00:43:42.086 line:90%
Please help her.

00:43:44.171 --> 00:43:46.090 line:90%
Please save my daughter.

00:43:48.884 --> 00:43:50.094 line:90%
My sins

00:43:51.679 --> 00:43:52.805 line:90%
put…

00:43:53.305 --> 00:43:55.224 line:90%
put my daughter in danger.

00:43:55.307 --> 00:43:56.434 line:90%
Your Highness.

00:44:02.773 --> 00:44:04.483 line:90%
<i>Please save her…</i>

00:44:06.819 --> 00:44:08.237 line:90%
<i>from that ak-gwi.</i>

00:44:19.290 --> 00:44:20.749 line:90%
<i>Princess!</i>

00:44:25.337 --> 00:44:26.714 line:90%
<i>Get a hold of yourself.</i>

00:44:29.300 --> 00:44:32.178 line:90%
To fight the spirit of the Crown Prince,

00:44:32.261 --> 00:44:34.263 line:90%
you must first regain your senses.

00:44:34.763 --> 00:44:35.848 line:90%
Do you hear me?

00:47:56.757 --> 00:48:00.010 line:90%
Subtitle translation by: Yun-hee Jang